TOMATO SAUCE: (TOMATOES (TOMATO, SALT, CITRIC ACID), OREGANO, BASIL, SUGAR, GARLIC POWDER, SALT, RED PEPPER FLAKES) SAUSAGE: PORK, WATER, SPICES, SALT, DEXTROSE, GARLIC POWDER, PAPRIKA PEPPERONI: BHA, BHT WITH CITRIC ACID ADDED TO HELP PROTECT FLAVOR, PORK AND BEEF, SALT, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF WATER, DEXTROSE, SPICES, LACTIC ACID STARTER CULTURE,OLEORESIN OF PAPRIKA, GARLIC POWDER, SODIUM NITRITE, BHA, BHT, CITRIC ACID.
